<div class="gfc-box get-prize">
  <div class="prize-banner"></div>
  <div class="prize-content-bg">
    <div class="prize-content">

      <p>您在本次宝箱游戏中获得奖励<span><%= (@betting.amount * @betting.odds).to_i %></span>钻币<br/>
        获得<span><%= ranking_config_item&.price&.to_i %></span><%= rank_item_name(ranking_config_item) %>
      </p>
      <div class="num-box"><%= image_tag "h5/images/num-#{@ranking_config.ranking}.png", alt: ''  %></div>
      <button id="btn" class="<%= wechat_browser? ? 'wechat' : '' %>" data-img="share-success-box">分享并领取奖励</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%unless wechat_browser? %>
<script>
  UrlCopy("btn", "<%=@share_config[:link_url]%>")
</script>
<%end%>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  $(".wechat").click()
})
</script>
